For the city of Denver, CO. Enter specific Adress or click on a certain location on the interactive map, the app will show the amenities available within a max distance of 5 miles (adjustable to less).
The amenities inclide: libraries, swimming pools, parks, playgrounds, and picnic areas. 
URL: https://mooc01.maps.arcgis.com/apps/instant/nearby/index.html?appid=93e055c5f9164f7a9d345a908192a646 
